### AP-7: Never copy code between entry points

**BAD** — duplicating gate logic across CLI and ACP:
```rust
// roko-cli/src/run.rs
async fn cli_run_gates() { /* 50 lines */ }
// roko-acp/src/runner.rs
async fn acp_run_gates() { /* same 50 lines, slightly different */ }
```

**GOOD** — shared service:
```rust
